column5: the second hen looks like a tanker
Quality chrome right there ladies and gentlemen!

She was and Angelo did a Great job with that fish,..when she was in the water,..we thought well over 10lb...but once banked,..we figured 8-9...belly about to burst with eggs,..so we let her swim and put those big genes to work!!!  More fish hit on artificials than roe today, by far..!!!
One more from this morning,..I think Im done until we get some fresh fish or dropbacks
